title: The Final Bosman [Ep. 00(Pilot)-20] WEBRip 720p
description:
The Final Bosman is the name of Kyle Bosman's gaming-oriented web show that started in mid 2013 with weekly episodes uploaded to gametrailers.com every Wednesday up until the site's closure in early February of 2016. Kyle has always strived to make the show about expressing his own opinions instead of going with the crowd. He initially started the show with the ambition of making an actually optimistic videogame-oriented show on the internet. This was done to contrast the plethora of videos with some guy in his late 20's to early 40's ranting about recent videogame controversies and scandals.

Due to the loyal following Kyle had created through The Final Bosman and the unfortunate closure of his video platform GameTrailers, I only find it fitting to archive his show, in the fear that most of his episodes (which are primarily uploaded to GameTrailers) will be deleted along with the website that hosted them
